org.plasma.provisioning.cli

Class UMLTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.plasma.provisioning.cli.ProvisioningTool
      • org.plasma.provisioning.cli.UMLTool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RDBConstants

    public class UMLTool
extends ProvisioningTool
implements RDBConstants
    The Unified Modeling Language (UML) Tool is used to provision UML modeling artifacts from various sources.

    Usage: java <@link org.plasma.provisioning.cli.UMLTool> Option Description ------ ---------- --dest [File] the fully qualified tool output destination file or directory name --dialect the vocabulary or usage which is characteristic for this context - used when sourceType is rdb - one of [oracle, mysql] is expected --help prints help on this tool --namespaces a comma separated list of namespace URIs --platform the UML modeling or other platform for this context - one of [papyrus, magicdraw] is expected --schemas a comma separated list of schema names --silent whether to log or print no messages at all (typically for testing) --sourceType a qualifier describing the input source - one of [xsd, rdb] is expected --verbose whether to log or print detailed messages
